#: ../../source/kv_cache/p2p_sharing.rst:4
msgid "P2P KV Cache Sharing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/kv_cache/p2p_sharing.rst:6
msgid ""
"P2P (Peer-to-Peer) KV cache sharing enables direct cache transfer between"
" multiple serving engine instances without requiring a centralized cache "
"server. This approach provides high-performance cache sharing with "
"reduced latency and improved scalability, especially beneficial in "
"distributed inference scenarios."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/kv_cache/p2p_sharing.rst:8
msgid ""
"LMCache supports P2P sharing through a controller-based architecture "
"using NIXL (NVIDIA Inference Xfer Library) for optimized data transfer "
"between instances."
msgstr ""

